name: TECHNOKING OF TESLA, IMPERATOR OF MARS
description:
Technoking of Tesla, Imperator of Mars, the Dogefather, the Rocketman, Elon Musk. Love him or hate him, he's one of the most influential people of our generation.

This piece is a nod to some of his biggest achievements: Tesla and SpaceX.

Artwork information:
128x128 pixels, scaled to 512x512
729 frame loop, 30fps, 2021
